Package pkg_gameobjects

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Character
    Character Class - Handles all the NPC of the Game
    Door
    Door Class - Creates doors, so we can lock them
    GameEngine
    GameEngine Class - The main class that creates the Player Object and contains all the printX() commands, creates the rooms, sets their items, also holds the commands and their correspondings
    MovingCharacter
    MovingCharacter Class - Handles all the moving NPCs of the Game
    Player
    Player Class - Holds all the informations about the Player (his current room, his inventory, the visited rooms and the weight he is carrying
